and ignited a passion.

00:02:59.620 --> 00:03:01.120
SUBJECT 1: Sports
is very important.

00:03:01.120 --> 00:03:03.110
It's where I go to
relax, and that's

00:03:03.110 --> 00:03:06.080
what I do to get
everything off my mind.

00:03:06.080 --> 00:03:07.840
I've learned to be
confident in myself,

00:03:07.840 --> 00:03:09.570
I've learned to be positive.

00:03:09.570 --> 00:03:10.480
I'm different.

00:03:10.480 --> 00:03:13.030
That's not a bad thing.

